data.title: A bird in a gilded cage
data.text:
Description

Gift of Dr. Mary Jane Esplen... starring Ann Sothern ; with George Murphy, Robert Sterling, Virginia O'Brien and Natalie Thompson ; original screen play by Mary C. McCall, Jr. ; directed by Edwin L.
